## Completed Work This Session

### slugsmith: Full project implementation (Tasks #409-412)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/slugsmith
Modern, zero-dependency Python URL slug generator replacing python-slugify (62M downloads/month).

**Phase 1 — Scaffolding:** pyproject.toml (MIT, src layout, Python >=3.9, hatchling), CI/CD workflows (Python 3.9-3.13), Makefile, dependabot. Lowered pytest to >=8.0 for 3.9 compat.

**Phase 2 — Transliteration:** CHAR_MAP covering Latin Extended, Cyrillic (Russian+Ukrainian), Greek, Arabic, Hebrew, special symbols. NFKD decomposition fallback. Language-specific maps: de, tr, pl, cs, fi, sv.

**Phase 3 — Core slugify():** Full python-slugify parameter compat (separator, lowercase, max_length, word_boundary, save_order, stopwords, regex_pattern, replacements, allow_unicode, lang). Pre-compiled regexes.

**Phase 4 — Tests:** 87 tests (33 core API, 20 transliteration, 23 compat, 2 smoke). mypy --strict clean. CI green.

